<item>
            <title>[LU-17362] Update ZFS version to 2.1.15</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17362</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Was it considered to update ZFS to 2.1.14 from 2.1.11 before the next Lustre releases? ZFS 2.1.14 is the latest of the 2.1.x releases.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;I hope it is not too late now that v2_15 is already at 2.15.4-RC1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Changes:&lt;/p&gt;

